<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.3150663>
    dc:description "FIGURE 6. Photos in life of (A) Cnemaspis yercaudensis, male NCBS-BH678, (B) Cnemaspis yercaudensis, female BNHS 2534, (C) Cnemaspis thackerayi sp. nov., holotype male NCBS-BH670, (D) Cnemaspis thackerayi sp. nov., female, uncollected individual, (E) Cnemaspis shevaroyensis sp. nov., holotype male NCBS-BH674, (F) Cnemaspis shevaroyensis sp. nov., paratype female BNHS 2529; all from Yercaud on the Shevaroy massif, Salem district, Tamil Nadu, India." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/3150663/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

